subject: Lead Time Microservice
description:
As a project manager, I would like to view the lead time of a user story so that I can understand the performance of a team  
  
Acceptance Criteria :   
1) Given I send a request with a Project ID and User Story ID, then compute and return the Lead time in JSON format so that I may know the lead time of a user story

subject: Lead time Microservice Status messages
description:
As a project manager, I would like to get specific error codes with specific error messages when data validation fails so that I may know when I input the wrong data

Acceptance Criteria :    
Given a request is sent to lead time micro service, then return : 200 Status code when there is a success response, or 401 when authorisation token is invalid, or 404 when Project ID does not exist, or 404 when user story is not found so that I may know when there is an issue.

subject: Cycle Time Microservice
description:
As a project manager, I would like to view the cycle time of a user story so that I can understand the performance and efficiency of a team to identify issues

Acceptance Criteria :    
1) Given I send a request with a Project slug, then compute and return the cycle time in JSON format so that I may know the cycle time of a user story

subject: Throughput Microservice
description:
As a project manager, I would like to view the throughput of a team so that I can understand the performance and efficiency of a team to identify any bottlenecks and issues of the team  
  
Acceptance Criteria :    
1) Given I send a request with a project slug, then compute and return the throughput in JSON format so that I may know the throughput of the team

description: As a developer, I would like the API code to be unit tested so that I may know when there are any defects in the code
